node.text:
Running free like the wind in Iceland 🇮🇸 We can promote your photos in our account. Check the link in our bio for instructions: @planetfervor

Who would you share this experience with? 🐎

📽 @hekluhestar
📍 Iceland
🎶 Sia - Unstoppable

node.text:
Which of these colorful birds is your favorite? 😍 We can promote your photos in our account. Check the link in our bio for instructions: @planetfervor

From 1 to 10? 🦜🎨

Names and Photos: 
1. Silver throated Tanager @jeffreypatrickkarnes
2. European Starling @raheel.aazim
3. Mandarin duck @eccentricwildlife
4. Golden-tailed Sapphire @birddetective
5. Strawberry Finch @praharsha_wildlife_stories
6. Periquito-rico @macrotake
7. European Bee-eater @dorugroza
8. Pink Robin @ravi_arora
9. Keel billed Toucan @floriankusterwildlife
10. Oriental Dwarf Kingfisher @rahul_belsare

Tag someone you would like you take a ride on this enchanting train with 👇 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @planetfervor

📽 @viajeroscallejeros
📍Switzerland

Save this for reference! 

𝐑𝐨𝐮𝐭𝐞
• Lugano/Bellinzona to Flüelen by train. Flüelen to Lucerne by steamboat or modern motor vessel “Diamant”. Applicable vice versa.

𝐑𝐨𝐮𝐭𝐞 𝐡𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐥𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬
• Lucerne City
• Rütli
• Rigi
• Tell's Chapel/Tell's Slab
• Flüelen (interchange station)
• Wassen Church
• Loop tunnels
• Giornico
• Bellinzona castles
• Lugano

𝐃𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞: 182 km
